==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unshed
<hw>Un*shed"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
parted or divided, as the hair.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not spilt, or made to flow, as blood or tears.</def>
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unshell</ent>⟦br⟧
